arts.ttl: Dybala double sends Roma to Europa League last 16 as Alkmaar also advances
arts.sum: Alkmaar advanced after a 2-2 draw with Galatasaray that saw the Dutch club reach the next round on a 6-3 aggregate score. Paulo Dybala struck twice in four minutes as Roma beat Porto 3-2 to reach the Europa League round of 16 on Thursday.
